## id: pulsar-admin-console
## name: Pulsar Admin Console Panel - Detect
## author: hack007x
## severity: info
## tags: panel,pulsar,console,admin,apache,discovery
## description: Pulsar admin console panel was detected.
## affects: pulsar
## shodan-query: title:"Pulsar Admin Console",http.title:"pulsar admin ui",http.title:"pulsar admin console"
